{{obsolete}}

{{flavour|After chanting for a brief time, the caster unleashes a fire storm on their target.}}

'''Chant Fire Storm''' is a monsters-only spell which functions much like the spell [[Fire Storm]], blasting an area with heavy, unavoidable, partially irresistible [[fire]] damage. However, unlike that spell, it takes a significant amount of time to complete, only activating 30 [[aut]]s after the caster begins to cast it.

The following monsters can cast Chant Fire Storm:

{{monsterlink|Salamander stormcaller}}

==History==
This spell was removed in [[0.18]]. Salamander stormcallers got Fire Storm instead.

Chant Fire Storm was added in [[0.17]].
